5000|$|The [...] "recognition" [...] of a <b>foreign</b> <b>judgment</b> {{occurs when}} the court of one country or {{jurisdiction}} accepts a judicial decision made by the courts of another [...] "foreign" [...] country or jurisdiction, and issues a judgment in substantially identical terms without rehearing {{the substance of the}} original lawsuit.|$|E
